gvs/src/gvslib/CHANGES

11/22/02
----------------------------------------------------
1. D. Silberstein corrected computation of bounding coordinates in
   gvs_metadata.c

10/16/01
----------------------------------------------------
1. Modified  gvs_metadata.c to use product version number from metadata file
   for level 3 HDF.

5/09/00
----------------------------------------------------
* Fixed Y2K bug.

v1.12 (??/99) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.13
----------------------------------------------------
1. Moved files from ../utils that make the library, to here.
2. Makes only libgvs.a
3. Grabbed the hdf routines from rsl-v1.24.1.

v1.11 (8/13/98) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.9
----------------------------------------------------
* Incremented P2A53_ALG_VERSION to 2.

v1.10 (5/29/98) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.6
----------------------------------------------------
* Ported to HP.
* get_info_from_file accepts compressed HDF file.
* Requires gv_utils-v1.5
* Doesnot read lat/lon info from  $GVS_DATA_PATH/gv_radar_lat_lon.data --
* Read lat/lon info from  $GVS_DATA_PATH/gv_radar_lat_lon.data 
* Removed some options in metadata_file and added more parameters to
  set_l2_specific_metadata().
* Added the capability for uninstalling the software.

v1.9 (1/26/98) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.5
----------------------------------------------------
* Added level_2_create_empty_granule_hdf.c.
* Minor mods in 'hdf_metadata.c.'.
* Requires gv_utils-v1.2.tgz 
* Added 'get_info_from_file.c'
* Added more comments in 'gvs_sat_coin.c'.

v1.8 (12/08/97) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.4
----------------------------------------------------
* Added more function in hdf_metadata.c
* get_radar_name_from_file.c will return site name correspondent to TSDIS'
  naming convention instead of radar's name.

v1.7 (11/18/97) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.3
----------------------------------------------------
* Fixed bug w.r.t. setting metadata field (num of vos).

v1.6 (11/13/97) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.2
----------------------------------------------------
* Added some more time functions in gvs_time.h,c
* More gvs_time.{h,c}, construct_time_in_seconds.c 
   and gvs_utilities.pl outside of gvs (to gv_utils)--
  so use -lgv_utils.
* Removed Perl requirement.
* Renamed gvs_utilities.{h,c} to gvs_sat_coin.{h,c}.

v1.5 (10/24/97) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.1
--------------------------------------------------
* Changed variable names in the routines that get satellite coincident data.
* Removed qa_param_name from metadata structure.
* Changed the interface of set_l2_specific_metadata().

v1.4 (10/10/97)  initially packaged w/ gvs pre-v4.1
--------------------------------------------------
* Added more programs
* Added more lib. routines, especially for level 3.
* Fixed bug (set metadata field, num vos, to 1 for single vos);
* Added new metadata field: radar wave length and anomaly flag.

v1.3 (8/19/97)  initially packaged w/ gvs v4.0
------------------------------------------------
* Minor mod in get_radar_name_from_file.c.

v1.2 (8/5/97) -- Initially packaged with gvs v3.7
------------------------------------------------
* Added a new program: get_radar_name_from_file


v1.1 
-----------------------------------------------
* Added gvs_utilities.*, Makefile, gvs_time.*.
* Creates a library to be used by packages in gvs.

v1.0 (7/2/97) packed with gvs v3.5
---------------------------------
* Initially created.
